{"tid":1269466,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"苟活比一死更需要勇氣","createTime":"2019-06-30T14:43:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-30T15:56:47.000Z","uid":261044,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"18366f47d7b8189a504c49866f48a49ef713e8e6","tid":1269466,"uid":261044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T14:43:27.000Z","msg":"依幾個禮拜<br />\n無論係仆街政府定係老而不死嘅藍絲奴才<br />\n都帶俾我地各種屈辱<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">但係!</span></strong><br />\n我想講嘅係<br />\n唔該各位<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>留住一條命</strong></span><br />\n如果你真係想死<br />\n請死之前問一問自己<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">你甘心依一刻就死咩?</span></strong><br />\n仲有另一點<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">你甘心早過嗰D老野死?</span></strong><br />\n佢地睇到你死之後只會拍晒手掌<br />\n嗰D話死得好嘅人不為其數<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">你甘心喺佢地落地獄之前死?</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n忍受一切非常難<br />\n特別係當你日日都聽到各種抹黑、詆毀、嘲諷、辱罵<br />\n無恥嘅把戲不斷上演<br />\n固然係鬱結難消<br />\n但請緊記<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>You never walk alone<br />\nWhat doesn't kill you makes you stronger</strong></span>"},{"pid":"f4493c4438ba9e39f99972edc058d73cdecb9cc0","tid":1269466,"uid":261044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T15:56:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}